What do you got here ?

05:51.183 --> 05:53.751
"Organic eggs" ?

05:53.819 --> 05:55.753
"Tiger's milk."
What's that ?

05:55.821 --> 05:57.922
"Wheat germ oil."

05:57.990 --> 05:59.924
