This special,
it's important
to Michael and me.

07:01.153 --> 07:03.087
Yeah, because
it's tearin' the country down.

07:03.155 --> 07:07.392
That's what you like--
to watch a bunch of jerks
tearin' the country down.

07:07.459 --> 07:11.396
Pollution is a fact of life,
and it's not just America.
It's worldwide.

07:11.463 --> 07:15.133
This special
with Jack lemmon--
leave me alone about that.

07:15.200 --> 07:17.635
And you know what you can do
with your Jack lemmon.

07:17.702 --> 07:20.971
And you know what you can do
with your John Wayne.
What about John Wayne ?

07:21.040 --> 07:22.973
Before you say anything,
let me warn you.

07:23.042 --> 07:24.975
