in his whole body.

08:32.711 --> 08:35.145
Nuts to you.
You don't believe me ?

08:35.214 --> 08:37.347
Maybe you'll believe
the Duke himself.
What ?

08:37.416 --> 08:40.851
Excuse me, young lady.
You just happen
to be sitting here.

08:40.919 --> 08:45.689
Would you be kind enough
to ask Mr. John Wayne
the question ?

08:45.757 --> 08:48.692
Mr. Wayne, is it true that
any one of those guys...

08:48.760 --> 08:51.695
Got more brains
in his little finger...

08:51.763 --> 08:54.165
Than you've got
in your whole body ?

08:54.233 --> 08:56.667
[ Imitating John Wayne ]
I'm afraid so, ma'am.

08:57.736 --> 08:59.670
Very, very funny.

08:59.738 --> 09:01.672
