with the groceries.

09:18.624 --> 09:21.559
Oh, the air mail stamps.
They're for Michael.
Oh, good.

09:21.627 --> 09:24.562
I can mail my letter today,
it'll get to Washington
by Monday.

09:24.630 --> 09:27.064
Washington ?
Are you writing
to Washington ?

09:27.132 --> 09:29.267
That's right.
Michael wrote
the president.

09:29.334 --> 09:31.536
Writin' to the president ?
About what ?

09:31.603 --> 09:34.038
All the things
we've been talking about--

09:34.105 --> 09:37.041
the pollution of our air,
the pollution of our water,

09:37.108 --> 09:40.545
the way us housewives
have no protection from
foods without nutrition,

09:40.612 --> 09:43.548
how they make products
with harmful things in 'em.

09:43.615 --> 09:47.685
You saw what happened
to Michael from that shirt.
[ Laughs ] He got a rash.

09:47.752 --> 09:51.689
