you have the nerve...

09:54.759 --> 09:57.861
To write to the president
of the United States
about your rash ?

09:57.929 --> 10:02.466
[ Sighs ]
Maybe he knows
a good skin man.

10:04.102 --> 10:06.036
I didn't write
about a rash.

10:06.104 --> 10:09.039
It's like Gloria said.
I wrote about
a lot of things--

10:09.107 --> 10:11.942
pollution, race relations,
the war in Vietnam.

10:12.010 --> 10:15.179
The war in Vietnam ?
You'd better let me
see that letter.
No, no.

10:15.247 --> 10:18.182
This is sealed.
It's private and personal
between the president and me.

10:18.250 --> 10:21.185
I demand to know
the contents of that letter.
It's between Nixon and me.

10:21.253 --> 10:23.187
<i>President</i> Nixon.
What's wrong
with plain "Nixon" ?

10:23.255 --> 10:26.190
Look in the paper.
They do it all the time--
Nixon this, Nixon that.

10:26.258 --> 10:29.193
That's their business,
but in this house
we show the proper respect.

10:29.261 --> 10:31.729
You don't like
"president Nixon,"
call him "Mr. Nixon."

10:31.796 --> 10:33.497
Or tricky dicky.

10:33.565 --> 10:35.666
<i>What ?</i>

10:40.672 --> 10:43.040
