he was a civilian,

10:47.112 --> 10:50.414
who now happens to be
commander-in-chief
of the United States.

10:50.482 --> 10:52.750
And he's doin'
a good job of it too.

10:52.817 --> 10:54.752
Let me tell you somethin',
wise guy.

10:54.819 --> 10:57.755
Mr. Nixon didn't
get us into Vietnam,
he inherited it,

10:57.822 --> 11:01.259
just like he inherited
inflation and integration
and pollution.

11:01.326 --> 11:04.295
Or are you gonna tell me
that Mr. Nixon
invented pollution ?

11:04.363 --> 11:06.430
No. But what's he
doing about it ?

11:06.498 --> 11:08.532
[ Mocking ]
"What's he doing about it ?"

11:08.600 --> 11:12.035
