Washington, D.C. bein' one
of your major cities--

11:19.378 --> 11:22.647
would you say
the drinking water there
is becomin' unsafe ?
Yeah.

11:22.714 --> 11:24.682
Well, that's where
I got both of youse.

11:24.750 --> 11:28.686
