in Washington, D.C.
is becomin' unsafe,

11:28.754 --> 11:32.189
do you think that Mr. Nixon
would let tricia drink it ?

11:35.594 --> 11:37.795
You can't answer that, can you ?
[ Chuckles ]

11:37.862 --> 11:40.298
I'll tell you somethin',
wise guy.

11:40.365 --> 11:43.801
You see,
you don't understand
your basic simplistics.

11:43.868 --> 11:47.805
Your biggest problems
always burn themselves down
to the human factor.

11:47.872 --> 11:51.309
I mean to say
the president, after all,
is only a man.

11:51.376 --> 11:54.512
Right, and he's
in the wrong job.

11:54.579 --> 11:57.515
Is that what you said to him
in that letter ?
Give me that.

11:57.582 --> 12:00.618
A pipsqueak like you,
you have the nerve to insult
the commander-in-chief--

12:00.686 --> 12:03.187
that's my return address
on there.

12:03.254 --> 12:06.357
<i>You're insultin'</i>
<i>president Nixon</i>
<i>from my return address ?</i>

12:06.425 --> 12:08.693
You must have
a screw loose.

12:08.760 --> 12:11.061
You left-wing, radical,
liberal, meatheaded polack !

12:11.129 --> 12:14.064
Give me the letter !
You're not gettin' this.
No, no !

12:14.132 --> 12:16.066
Come on, daddy !
Oh, no !

12:16.134 --> 12:19.069
