Oh, no !

12:19.137 --> 12:21.071
Hold it !
Hold it !

12:21.139 --> 12:25.209
This letter gets mailed
from this house
over my dead body.

12:31.717 --> 12:34.652
All right, Archie,
enough's enough.
Just give me the letter.

12:34.720 --> 12:37.655
You're tampering with
the United States mail, daddy.
That's a federal offense.

12:37.723 --> 12:40.157
So is
excitement to riot.

12:40.225 --> 12:42.159
The letter--

12:42.227 --> 12:45.162
the letter is not gonna
<i>incite</i> anyone to riot.

12:45.230 --> 12:48.165
The letter
is between a citizen
and his government.

12:48.233 --> 12:51.268
I've heard you say it
a hundred times, Archie--
the government works for me.

12:51.336 --> 12:54.772
That's right. I said,
"the government works for me."
Not you, meathead.

12:56.107 --> 12:58.676
The government works for
taxpayers and breadwinners...

12:58.744 --> 13:00.678
And people who
contribute to society.

13:00.746 --> 13:03.681
You're such a contributor,
why don't you write a letter
to the president ?

13:03.749 --> 13:05.683
Because I got nothin'
to beef about.

13:05.751 --> 13:07.685
I knew
you'd cop out, daddy.

13:07.753 --> 13:11.121
You just talk,
that's all.
I'll tell you what I'll do--

13:11.189 --> 13:14.124
