sign the letter.
I wouldn't have neither.

13:21.700 --> 13:24.134
Edith, I told you
to stifle yourself !

13:24.202 --> 13:26.136
You gonna write
to the president ?

13:26.204 --> 13:28.138
Yes, I am !
Good.

13:28.206 --> 13:31.141
