the mailbox before yours.

13:39.885 --> 13:43.220
That way,
the president reads mine first,
he'll be able to stomach yours.

13:43.288 --> 13:47.858
Edith, uh,
get me our embossed
personal stationery.

13:47.926 --> 13:51.194
You know, with the initials
intertwined on the top.

13:51.262 --> 13:54.432
