no writing paper
like that.

13:54.499 --> 13:56.934
Edith,
our personal stationery.

13:57.001 --> 14:00.237
It was a gift from
that no-neck cousin of yours
works for w.T. Grant.

14:00.305 --> 14:02.239
You know,
a wedding present.

14:02.307 --> 14:04.708
Oh, Archie,

14:04.776 --> 14:08.045
for heaven's sake,
that was 22 years ago.

14:08.112 --> 14:11.381
What difference does it make
how long ago it was, huh ?

14:11.450 --> 14:14.618
You save everything else.
You certainly must have
saved that.

14:14.686 --> 14:19.323
Edith, I can't write to the
President of the United States
unless I'm gonna do it right.

14:35.740 --> 14:38.175
